# Not part of the served site (Workers static assets upload filter).
# Leading slash anchors to the repo root so `/data/` does NOT also match
# `public/data/` (gitignore semantics: an unanchored `data/` matches at any depth).
/.github/
/data/
/db/
/docs/
/eval/
/ingestion/
/reports/
/scratch/
/frontend/components/
*.md
*.txt
*.py
/Procfile
/requirements.txt
/runtime.txt
/wrangler.jsonc
